ChatBotConverse is a conversational AI project aimed at simulating human-like interactions through text. Leveraging state-of-the-art natural language processing techniques, this project provides a platform for building intelligent chatbots capable of engaging in meaningful conversations with users.

Features:

Natural Language Understanding (NLU): Implementing advanced NLU models to comprehend user inputs accurately.
Contextual Understanding: Maintaining context across conversations to enable more coherent and relevant responses.
Multi-turn Dialogue Handling: Supporting multi-turn dialogues for fluid and seamless interactions.
Personalization: Incorporating mechanisms for chatbots to adapt their responses based on user preferences and history.
Emotion Recognition: Integrating emotion recognition models to imbue chatbots with emotional intelligence.
Extensibility: Providing an extensible framework for developers to easily add new features and functionalities.
